(6, 'Nikon Z6II Mirrorless Camera | Official Nikon USA Partner Model | Body FX-Format Full-Frame 4K UHD Video 1659 Bundle with Deco Gear Travel Bag Case + Extra Battery + Photography LED + Software Kit', 'nikon-z6ii-mirrorless-camera-official-nikon-usa-partner-model-body-fx-format-full-frame-4k-uhd-video-1659-bundle-with-deco-gear-travel-bag-case-extra-battery-photography-led-software-kit', 'uploads/media_678959017f66d.jpg', 2, 5, 9, 3, 4, 50, 'Nikon AUTHORIZED Model- Includes Full Nikon USA WARRANTY. Nikon Z 6II. True Multimedia Powerhouse. The most versatile Z series camera yet, balancing speed, power, low-light ability, and advanced video features. Features a 24.5-megapixel BSI CMOS sensor and dual EXPEED 6 Processors. Impressive ISO range from ISO 100-51,200, expandable up to ISO 204,800 equivalent. The Z 6II boasts a fast 14 fps continuous shooting speed, providing quick performance for capturing action.', '<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color: var(--__N4QdCheV6mGo,#0f1111);\">Nikon AUTHORIZED Model- Includes Full Nikon USA WARRANTY. Nikon Z 6II. True Multimedia Powerhouse. The most versatile Z series camera yet, balancing speed, power, low-light ability, and advanced video features. Features a 24.5-megapixel BSI CMOS sensor and dual EXPEED 6 Processors. Impressive ISO range from ISO 100-51,200, expandable up to ISO 204,800 equivalent. The Z 6II boasts a fast 14 fps continuous shooting speed, providing quick performance for capturing action.</span></li><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color: var(--__N4QdCheV6mGo,#0f1111);\">Full frame. Full pixel readout. Full featured 4K UHD Video. Built with videographers in mind, the Z6 II is capable of a variety of frame rates, including 4K UHD 60p with full pixel readout, 4K 30p, as well as Full HD 120p for slow motion. The Z 6II’s AF speed and tracking sensitivity is adjustable to meet creative needs, while the focus ring is also reversible. | Dual card slots (CFexpress/XQD + UHS-II SD) provide flexibility when shooting important moments such as weddings and events.</span></li><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color: var(--__N4QdCheV6mGo,#0f1111);\">The Z 6II’s enhanced AF system features 273 on-sensor phase-detect autofocus points for easy subject acquisition and tracking throughout the frame, including at the edges. The Z 6II easily acquires focus in extreme low light scenarios (down to -4.5 EV5) , making it an ideal option for capturing nightscapes and events. The Z 6II also supports Eye-Detection AF and Animal-Detection AF with video recording, enabling continuous focus on the eyes of humans, dogs, and cats.</span></li><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color: var(--__N4QdCheV6mGo,#0f1111);\">CAMERA INCLUDES: Nikon Z6II Mirrorless Camera Full Frame FX-format Body Only 1659 | EN-EL15c Rechargeable Li-ion Battery | MH-25a Battery Charger | EH-7p Charging AC Adapter | UC-E24 USB Cable | HDMI/USB Cable Clip | BS-1 Accessory Shoe Cover | AN-DC19 Strap | BF-N1 Body Cap | DK-29 Rubber Eyecup | Nikon USA Authorized Warranty</span></li><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color: var(--__N4QdCheV6mGo,#0f1111);\">BUNDLE INCLUDES: Deco Gear Camera Gadget Bag Travel Case | Lexar Professional 667x 64GB SDXC UHS-3 Class 10 Memory Card | Compatible Battery for EN-EL15 | Corel Paint Shop Pro &amp; VideoSuite Software |