(23, 'Dell XPS 9530 Laptop (2023) | 15.6\" FHD+ | Core i7-512GB SSD - 32GB RAM - Arc A370M | 14 Cores @ 5GHz - 13th Gen CPU Win 11 Home', 'dell-xps-9530-laptop-2023-156-fhd-core-i7-512gb-ssd-32gb-ram-arc-a370m-14-cores-at-5ghz-13th-gen-cpu-win-11-home', 'uploads/media_678a0f9fc7bae.jpg', 9, 5, 7, 5, 6, 45, 'Latest and Best: Released in 2023 The XPS 9530 is the latest version of Dell in the 15\" XPS family and comes with all the latest technology, including DDR4 memory with clock frequency at 3200MHz and a 13th generation Intel 14-core processor. The fourteen cores of the Core i7-13700H processor enable exceptional multitasking. To save power and extend battery life, the processor will run at 3.7GHz under low use, but will boost to 5GHz under heavy use for powerful performance', '<h1 class=\"a-size-base-plus a-text-bold\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 4px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); font-family: &quot;Amazon Ember&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px !important; line-height: 24px !important;\">About this item</h1><ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Amazon Ember&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color: var(--__N4QdCheV6mGo,#0f1111);\">Latest and Best: Released in 2023 The XPS 9530 is the latest version of Dell in the 15\" XPS family and comes with all the latest technology, including DDR4 memory with clock frequency at 3200MHz and a 13th generation Intel 14-core processor. The fourteen cores of the Core i7-13700H processor enable exceptional multitasking. To save power and extend battery life, the processor will run at 3.7GHz under low use, but will boost to 5GHz under heavy use for powerful performance</span></li