_CR0,0,970,600_PT0_SX970_V1___.jpg\" style=\"max-width: 100%; border: 0px; vertical-align: top; margin-bottom: 14px !important;\"><p class=\"a-spacing-base\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px !important;\"><span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight: 700 !important;\">Go farther, play longer, create better.</span></p><p class=\"a-spacing-base\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px !important;\">Lightweight design, advanced cooling, 71Wh battery, USB-C Fast Charge for gaming and creating on the go.</p><p class=\"a-spacing-base\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px !important;\"><span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight: 700 !important;\">Less AI talk, more AI performance.</span></p><p class=\"a-spacing-base\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px !important;\">Intel Core Ultra Processor, NVIDIA GeForce RTX 40 series GPUs with AI DLSS3.5, ray tracing – no vague promises, just performance.</p><p class=\"a-spacing-base\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px !important;\"><span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight: 700 !important;\">Your best work deserves the best display.</span></p><p class=\"a-spacing-base\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px !important;\">Experience 3D rendering, video editing, AAA gaming in full color and clarity – 2.8K 120Hz OLED, 0.2ms response, 100% DCI-P3.</p><p class=\"a-spacing-base\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px !important;\"><span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight: 700 !important;\">We\'re in this together.</span></p><p class=\"a-spacing-base\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px !important;\">Doing our part with recycled materials, and EPEAT Gold with Climate+ and ENERGY STA