ites are lightning fast in macOS, including Microsoft Excel and PowerPoint, Adobe Creative Cloud and Google Workspace. And free software updates keep things running smoothly and securely. (Apps are available on the App Store. Title availability is subject to change.)</span></li><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color: var(--__N4QdCheV6mGo,#0f1111);\">ADVANCED CAMERA AND AUDIO — Look sharp and sound great with a 1080p FaceTime HD camera and three-mic array. Immerse yourself in movies and music with a six-speaker sound system and Spatial Audio.</span></li><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color: var(--__N4QdCheV6mGo,#0f1111);\"><div id=\"centerCol\" class=\"centerColAlign\" style=\"margin-right: 300px; margin-left: 753.95px;\"><div id=\"atfCenter15_feature_div\" class=\"celwidget\" data-feature-name=\"atfCenter15\" data-csa-c-type=\"widget\" data-csa-c-content-id=\"atfCenter15\" data-csa-c-slot-id=\"atfCenter15_feature_div\" data-csa-c-asin=\"B0C75NW3L9\" data-csa-c-is-in-initial-active-row=\"false\" data-cel-widget=\"atfCenter15_feature_div\" data-csa-c-id=\"l4pm6c-ukah1h-9sr8xw-yczkb6\"><div id=\"\" class=\"content-grid-alternate-styles mako-v2\" style=\"position: relative; margin: 0px auto; background-size: cover; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><div class=\"content-grid-row-wrapper \" data-lazy-loading-background-image=\"\" style=\"position: relative; margin: 15px auto 15px 0px; background-size: cover; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; clear: none; font-size: 16px; line-height: 21px; max-width: 480px;\"><div class=\"a-row\" style=\"width: 410.05px; max-height: inherit;\"><div class=\"content-grid-col-wrapper override-column-sp