ass=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color: var(--__N4QdCheV6mGo,#0f1111);\">【STURDY AND NOISELESS】 The twin bed frame with LED lights is crafted with durability in mind, featuring 11 stable metal slats and 9 thick legs for superior stability. The metal frame ensures long-lasting sturdiness, with tested connections to guarantee a secure and reliable sleeping experience. It is carefully engineered to distribute weight evenly, minimizing movement or wobbling.</span></li><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color: var(--__N4QdCheV6mGo,#0f1111);\">【MODERN MINIMALIST DESIGN】 The design of this twin bed frame can complement any decor style. The black color scheme makes it versatile and adaptable, while the storage space under the bed easily accommodates luggage, shoe boxes, and storage bins. Additionally, the robotic vacuum can easily navigate through, keeping your bedroom clean and organized.</span></li><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color: var(--__N4QdCheV6mGo,#0f1111);\">【NO BOX SPRING NEEDED】 The twin bed frame can be quickly assembled without the need for bulky box springs or any additional foundations. The mattress stays securely in place, helping to extend the lifespan of memory foam, latex, or spring mattresses (mattress not included).</span></li><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color: var(--__N4QdCheV6mGo,#0f1111);\">【QUICK ASSEMBLY AND WARRANTY】 All necessary parts and tools for assembling the twin bed frame are included in one box, along with very detailed printed instructions. One person can assemble the bed frame in under 30 minutes. If you encounter any missing or damaged parts