(102, 'Aeac Smart Watch (Answer/Make Call) for Men Women,1.8\" Fitness Watch for iPhone iOS Andriod with Blood Oxygen/Stress Monitor,100+ Sport Modes,Fitness Tracker IP68 Waterproof', 'aeac-smart-watch-answermake-call-for-men-women18-fitness-watch-for-iphone-ios-andriod-with-blood-oxygenstress-monitor100-sport-modesfitness-tracker-ip68-waterproof', 'uploads/media_678b7c06c7339.jpg', 1, 5, 20, NULL, 5, 666, '☎️【Alexa Built-in&Bluetooth 5.3 call Smart Watches】Talk to Amazon Alexa on your watches for men. Ask questions, play music, check the weather, set alarms and timers, and more just by speaking to your watch. With this Bluetooth call smart watch, you don\'t miss any important calls. You can make, answer and refuse a call on your wrist, also receive message/app notification, listening to music via the Android smart watch directly. Never miss a call and a message. (Note: Can\'t reply message) .', '<h1 class=\"a-size-base-plus a-text-bold\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 4px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); font-family: &quot;Amazon Ember&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px !important; line-height: 24px !important;\">About this item</h1><ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Amazon Ember&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color: var(--__N4QdCheV6mGo,#0f1111);\">☎️【Alexa Built-in&amp;Bluetooth 5.3 call Smart Watches】Talk to Amazon Alexa on your watches for men. Ask questions, play music, check the weather, set alarms and timers, and more just by speaking to your watch. With this Bluetooth call smart watch, you don\'t miss any important calls. You can make, answer and refuse a call on your wrist, also receive message/app notification, listening to music via the Android smart watch directly. Never miss a call and a message. (Note: Can\'t reply message) .</span></li><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color: var(--__N4QdCheV6mGo,#0f1111);\">💕【All-day Health&amp;Activity Monitoring 】The fitness watch for women give you real-time heart rate, blood oxygen monitor (SpO2) which can also help to keep track of your sleep data and bring you to more scientific sleep habits. Record all-day activities like steps, calories burned, miles walked, active minutes. Gives deeper insights into your health. Besides, there is a Health trends. Keep wearing the device every day for more than 17days and you could see the trends.</span></li><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color: var(--__N4QdCheV6mGo,#0f1111);\">🏃【100+ Sport Modes &amp; IP68 waterproof】Smart watch for women supports 100+ sport modes, you can choose the corresponding mode according to your exercise: walking, running, cycling, soccer, basketball, swimming, rope skipping, badminton, etc., Connected to the cell phone APP can display speed, distance and record workout route, calories burned and exercise heart rate. It with IP68 waterproof and dust-proof, so you can use it when washing your hands or on rainy days.</span></li><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color: var(--__N4QdCheV6mGo,#0f1111);\">⌚【Long-lasting Battery Life &amp; More Practical Tools】It could last about 10 days when in auto monitoring mode for heart rate or 6 days when in the BT mode with a super large battery capacity (300mAh). This watch provides many other useful functions like alarm clocks, pedometer, world clocks, weather forecast, music control, timer, music controller, sedentary reminder, adjust brightness, find phone, noise, flashlight, intelligent motion recognition on running and walking, etc</span></li><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color: var(--__N4QdCheV6mGo,#0f1111);\">🌞【1.8\'\' 2.5D Screen &amp; 150+ Watch Faces】1.8-inch color full-touch 2.5D curved tempered glass HD large screen, gives excellent vivid image and displaying more information. The smart watch for women ensures smooth operations and 240*280 resolution for you. 150+ watch faces for you to choose from App: Veryfit. Even supports customized watch face as any photos from your phone such as your friends, family, pets, etc.</span></li><li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color: var(--__N4QdCheV6mGo,#0f1111);\"><div id=\"aplusBrandStory_feature_div\" class=\"celwidget pd_rd_w-1vMCJ pd_rd_r-10GDT825K0TCN3M2H81T pd_rd_wg-WYX78\" data-feature-name=\"aplusBrandStory\" data-csa-c-type=\"widget\" data-csa-c-content-id=\"aplusBrandStory\" data-csa-c-slot-id=\"aplusBrandStory_feature_div\" data-csa-c-asin=\"\" data-csa-c-is-in-initial-active-row=\"false\" data-csa-c-id=\"6fp7hz-441b65-g93m86-a60i5a\"><div id=\"aplus\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-large bucket\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><hr noshade=\"true\" size=\"1\" class=\"bucketDivider\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 19px; margin-top: 0px; filter: none; z-index: 0; zoom: 1; clear: left; background: 0px 0px !important; border-top-color: rgb(204, 204, 204) !important; height: 44px !important; margin-bottom: -36px !important;\"><h2 style=\"padding: 0px 0px 4px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; line-height: 32px; font-size: 21px !important; color: rgb(51, 51, 51) !important;\">From the brand</h2><div class=\"aplus-v2 desktop celwidget\" cel_widget_id=\"aplus\" data-csa-c